POLOKWANE – Mostly sunny and pleasant conditions are what residents in the city can expect this week.  AccuWeather’s forecast anticipates maximum temperatures in the high twenties, peaking in the low thirties over the weekend. Sunday (March 19) will be the warmest day of the week at 31ºC, while Monday to Wednesday will remain constant at 27ºC. Partly cloudy conditions are expected for the rest of the week with a thunderstorm expected this afternoon (March 13). No rain is forecast for the rest of the week. 